    <item>
      <title>欧洲将努力团结起来抵制特朗普的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-will-struggle-to-stand-united-against-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲大陆的许多领导人在国内承受着巨大的压力，以至于他们不具备在全球事务上采取果断行动的政治影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-will-struggle-to-stand-united-against-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲越来越乐观地认为特朗普不会放弃乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-grows-more-optimistic-trump-won-t-abandon-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的欧洲盟友谨慎乐观地认为，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普不会强迫基辅与俄罗斯进行过早谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/europe-grows-more-optimistic-trump-won-t-abandon-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾要求中国撤回靠近岸边的“怪物”船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/philippines-tells-china-to-withdraw-monster-ship-nearing-shore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾对一艘大型中国船只靠近其西海岸南海水域发出警报，这凸显了美国总统当选人唐纳德·特朗普就职前夕出现的新的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/philippines-tells-china-to-withdraw-monster-ship-nearing-shore</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 03:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回国前朝鲜试射短程导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/north-korea-fires-unidentified-projectile-seoul-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜周二向其东海岸海域发射数枚短程导弹，在唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫前不到一周的时间里，加剧了该地区的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/north-korea-fires-unidentified-projectile-seoul-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称特朗普团队正在考虑逐步征收关税，美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/dollar-falls-on-report-trump-team-mulling-gradual-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻社报道唐纳德·特朗普的新经济团队正在考虑逐步提高关税后，美元兑几乎所有主要货币均下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/dollar-falls-on-report-trump-team-mulling-gradual-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国军情五处文件显示，英国女王伊丽莎白二世并未被告知白金汉宫内有苏联间谍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-14/queen-elizabeth-ii-wasn-t-told-about-soviet-spy-in-her-palace-declassified-mi5-files-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦（美联社）——新解密的文件显示，女王伊丽莎白二世并未被告知其长期艺术顾问作为苏联间谍的双重生活的细节，因为宫廷官员不想增加她的忧虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-14/queen-elizabeth-ii-wasn-t-told-about-soviet-spy-in-her-palace-declassified-mi5-files-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:27:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森寻求 25 亿美元在洛杉矶实施“马歇尔计划”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/newsom-seeks-2-5-billion-for-marshall-plan-in-los-angeles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆希望州议员批准 25 亿美元资金，以协助紧急响应工作，并资助洛杉矶毁灭性山火的大规模恢复计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/newsom-seeks-2-5-billion-for-marshall-plan-in-los-angeles</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:16:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称“非常接近”达成以色列与哈马斯人质协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他相信谈判人员可以在下周一他就职之前达成停火协议，根据该协议，哈马斯将交出以色列人质，这是协议可能即将达成的最新信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/sullivan-cites-distinct-possibility-of-gaza-deal-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信概述重振泰国股市的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国执政党事实上的领导人他信·西那瓦呼吁加强监管监督、改善公司治理并向长期股票投资者提供税收优惠，以重振人们对该国低迷的股市的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/thaksin-outlines-steps-to-revive-flagging-thai-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应链转移致中国对越南出口首次超过日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国关税迫使企业寻找新的供应商以避免征税，同时继续依赖中国制造商提供零部件，越南首次超过日本成为中国第三大出口目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/china-exports-more-to-vietnam-than-japan-for-first-time-as-supply-chains-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
